body:
What is your IGN and team?
my in game name is zic_e also known as zicuri and my team is Horizon

How many tournaments have you participated in?
This is going to be our first tournament as a team

Any team in particular you'd like to face off against?
Well I would love to face PureDogs, since they are so confident I want to see how they play

Any team you don't want to face off against?
There is not a team that I dont want to face off but I dont want to face allah until finals

How do you think you'll do this time around?
I think we can do well at least top 3

Any teams you have a rivalry with?
No one tbh all teams are the same for us, there is a team called apollo that always want beef but meh

What do you think is your team's best strength, and your best strength alone?
Our best strength hmmm I think our pvp, and my best strength alone is oh my pvp :)

What do you think is your team's worst weakness, and your worst weakness alone?
Our worst weakness as a team is chemistry and my worst weakness alone is that I suck at leading

What have you done to prepare?
Nothing to be honest a few scrim but meh

Anything you'd like to say to your opponents?
Good luck and have fun, there is always a chance
squadcat will be top4 or 3 this tournament!
